== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2013年12月，[[布萊恩·辛格|布莱恩·辛格]]宣布，《[[X戰警：未來昔日|X戰警：未來昔日]]》的續集名為《X戰警：天啟》，並由[[賽門·金柏格|賽門·金柏格]]、{{link-en|丹·哈里斯|Dan Harris (screenwriter)}}和麥可·多爾蒂編劇<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.superherohype.com/news/316109-bryan-singer-confirmed-to-direct-x-men-apocalypse |title=Bryan Singer Confirmed to Direct X-Men: Apocalypse |author=Lesnick, Silas |date=September 22, 2014 |accessdate=September 23, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140925033210/http://www.superherohype.com/news/316109-bryan-singer-confirmed-to-direct-x-men-apocalypse |archive-date=2014-09-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據辛格所述，本集的重點都將放於變種人的起源<ref>{{cite web |url = http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/01/07/x-men-apocalypse-bryan-singer/ |title = X-Men: Apocalypse: Bryan Singer teases new film ‘will address mutant origins’ — EXCLUSIVE |access-date = 2014-10-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150128043744/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/01/07/x-men-apocalypse-bryan-singer/ |archive-date = 2015-01-28 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。辛格表示，這將背景1983年代的《[[X戰警：第一戰|X戰警：第一戰]]》完成一三部曲<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.theqandapodcast.com/?m=1 |title = The Q&A with Jeff Goldsmith: X-Men: Days of Future Past Q&A |work = The Q & A Podcast |date = June 13, 2014 |accessdate = June 13, 2014 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140715020221/http://www.theqandapodcast.com/?m=1 |archive-date = 2014-07-15 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://x-menfilms.com/simon-kinberg-x-men-apocalypse-completes-the-first-class-trilogy/ |title=Simon Kinberg: X-Men: Apocalypse Completes the First Class Trilogy |date=September 26, 2014 |accessdate=September 27, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140929140245/http://x-menfilms.com/simon-kinberg-x-men-apocalypse-completes-the-first-class-trilogy/ |archive-date=2014-09-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。演員[[詹姆斯·麥艾維|詹姆斯·麥艾維]]、[[麥可·法斯賓達|麥可·法斯賓達]]、[[尼可拉斯·霍特|尼可拉斯·霍特]]、[[珍妮佛·勞倫斯|珍妮佛·勞倫斯]]、[[伊凡·彼得斯|伊凡·彼得斯]]、[[盧卡斯·提爾|盧卡斯·提爾]]以及[[蘿絲·拜恩|蘿絲·拜恩]]和系列部分的原班人馬都將回歸演出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/04/11/x-men-apocalypse-new-details/ |title='X-Men: Apocalypse': Who will return? What new mutants may appear? Scoop on the next X-Men film -- Exclusive |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=April 11, 2014 |accessdate=April 11, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102124014/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/04/11/x-men-apocalypse-new-details/ |archive-date=2014-11-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/21/quicksilver-will-have-expanded-role-in-x-men-apocalypse |title=Quicksilver Will Have Expanded Role in X-Men: Apocalypse |work=IGN |author=Tilly, Chris |date=May 21, 2014 |accessdate=September 23, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924040425/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/21/quicksilver-will-have-expanded-role-in-x-men-apocalypse |archive-date=2014-09-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Stedman|first=Alex|title=Members of Original Cast to Appear in ‘X-Men: Apocalypse’|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/x-men-apocalypse-original-cast-bryan-singer-1201192868/|newspaper=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=June 1, 2014|date=May 26, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101200540/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/x-men-apocalypse-original-cast-bryan-singer-1201192868/|archive-date=2014-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而[[獨眼龍_(漫威漫畫)|獨眼龍]]、[[火鳳凰_(漫威漫畫)|火鳳凰]]和[[暴風女|暴風女]]也將現身於電影中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/x-men-apocalypse-will-star-cyclops-jean-grey-and-storm/ |title='X-Men: Apocalypse' Will Star Cyclops, Jean Grey and Storm |publisher=Sci-Fi Now |date=May 7, 2014 |accessdate=May 7, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019090535/http://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/x-men-apocalypse-will-star-cyclops-jean-grey-and-storm/ |archive-date=2014-10-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年11月24日，宣布[[奧斯卡·伊薩克|奧斯卡·伊薩克]]將於電影中飾演反派"[[天啟_(漫威漫畫)|天啟]]"<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscar-isaac-x-men-apocalypse-casting-1201342774/ |title='X-Men: Apocalypse': Oscar Isaac Nabs Villain Role |publisher=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]'' |date=November 24, 2014 |accessdate=November 24, 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141125020544/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscar-isaac-x-men-apocalypse-casting-1201342774/ |archive-date=2014-11-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年1月17日，宣布原版X教授演員[[派崔克·史都華|派崔克·史都華]]、萬磁王演員[[伊恩·麥克連|伊恩·麥克連]]將不會現身於電影中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/patrick-stewart-ian-mckellen-xmen-apocalypse-20150117 |title=Patrick Stewart, Ian McKellen Not Returning for Next 'X-Men' Film |date=January 17, 2015 |accessdate=January 17, 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119224629/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/patrick-stewart-ian-mckellen-xmen-apocalypse-20150117 |archive-date=2015-01-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年1月22日，辛格於自己的推特上宣布，[[泰·謝里丹|泰·謝里丹]]、[[蘇菲·特納|蘇菲·特納]]和[[雅莉珊卓·希普|雅莉珊卓·希普]]將分別飾演年輕版的[[獨眼龍_(漫威漫畫)|獨眼龍]]、[[火鳳凰_(漫威漫畫)|火鳳凰]]和[[暴風女|暴風女]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/x-men-apocalypse-will-star-cyclops-jean-grey-and-storm/|title='X-Men: Apocalypse' Will Star Cyclops, Jean Grey and Storm|publisher=Sci-Fi Now|date=May 7, 2014|accessdate=May 7, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019090535/http://www.scifinow.co.uk/news/x-men-apocalypse-will-star-cyclops-jean-grey-and-storm/|archive-date=2014-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[https://twitter.com/BryanSinger/status/55843750831567872]</ref>。2015年2月19日辛格宣布[[寇帝·史密-麥菲|寇帝·史密-麥菲]]演出年輕版藍魔鬼。同年3月，[[珍妮佛·勞倫斯|珍妮佛·勞倫斯]]表示本片將會是自己飾演[[魔形女|魔形女]]的最後一部<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/jennifer-lawrence-to-quit-x-men-franchise-after-apocalypse/1/425734.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326003007/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/jennifer-lawrence-to-quit-x-men-franchise-after-apocalypse/1/425734.html |archive-date=2015-03-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，[[拉娜·康多|拉娜·康多]]飾演[[歡歡_(漫畫)|歡歡]]，[[班·哈迪|班·哈迪]]則飾演[[天使_(漫威漫畫)|天使]]，[[靈蝶|靈蝶]]由[[奥利维亚·穆恩|奥利维亚·穆恩]]飾演。<ref name="BenAngel">{{cite news|last1=Hewitt|first1=Chris|title=Exclusive: Bryan Singer Confirms Ben Hardy Is Angel In X-Men: Apocalypse|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43949|accessdate=April 9, 2015|publisher=Empire|date=April 9, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150422165039/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=43949|archive-date=2015-04-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="OliviaPsylocke">{{cite web|last1=Singer|first1=Bryan|title=Bryan Singer on Instagram: "Excited to welcome @oliviamunn as Betsy Braddock! #Psylocke #XmenApocalypse #XMEN"|url=https://instagram.com/p/1bYchvxD_p/|accessdate=April 13, 2015|publisher=[[Instagram|Instagram]]|date=April 13, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150501093629/https://instagram.com/p/1bYchvxD_p/|archive-date=2015-05-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="LucasHavok">{{cite web|last1=Singer|first1=Bryan|title=Welcome back #lucastill #xmen #XmenApocalypse #jamesmcavoy #michaelfassbender #jenniferlawrence #nicholashoult #rosebyrne How time flies! #XmenFirstClass|url=https://instagram.com/p/1lxxZERDw4/|website=Instagram|accessdate=17 April 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401092639/https://www.instagram.com/p/1lxxZERDw4/|archive-date=2016-04-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

