己將不再執導該系列，但仍有回歸的機會<ref>{{cite web|last=Rottenberg|first=Josh|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-bryan-singer-xmen-apocalypse-20160526-snap-story.html|title='X-Men' director Bryan Singer reveals how he built the 'Apocalypse'|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=May 30, 2016|accessdate=May 30, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220152515/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-bryan-singer-xmen-apocalypse-20160526-snap-story.html|archive-date=2017-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年11月9日，金伯格向《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》表示，下一部《X戰警》電影將會是個軟重啟，他仍繼續參與劇本，而珍妮佛·勞倫斯、麥可·法斯賓達、尼可拉斯·霍特和詹姆斯·麥艾維仍樂觀性的能夠繼續出現<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/foxs-x-men-issues-jennifer-lawrence-unsigned-deadpool-defections-gambit-hold-945505|title=-Fox's X-Men Issues: Jennifer Lawrence Unsigned, 'Deadpool' Defections, 'Gambit' on Hold|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|last=Kit|first=Borys|date=November 9, 2016|access-date=2017-02-21|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qgyenQcB?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/foxs-x-men-issues-jennifer-lawrence-unsigned-deadpool-defections-gambit-hold-945505|archive-date=2017-05-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

